dataIdInfo.idAbs: This line data layer represents trails for Marinette County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Marinette_Trails_2018.gdb
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [The recreation trails feature class represents the motorized recreation trails as determined by the Marinette County Forestry and Parks Department.]
